keyFacts: The document is an email chain regarding FBI case LSI-08192019-327098-002.
A forensic accountant at the FBI New York Field Office requests a password for a CD related to the case.
Renae A. Rodriguez of the Litigation Support Unit in San Antonio provides the password.
The correspondence demonstrates internal FBI procedures for handling digital evidence in investigations.
The document references confidential material (SDNY_GM_00004177, EFTA 00118251, EFTA01265313).
